      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/vietnam-continues-support-bank-engulfed-massive-fraud-central-bank-says-2024-04-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南央行周五表示，将继续向西贡股份商业银行 (SCB) 提供支持，该银行在挤兑存款后于 2022 年 10 月将其置于特别监管之下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/vietnam-continues-support-bank-engulfed-massive-fraud-central-bank-says-2024-04-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 05:32:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
